title: Match History from S4 and S5
body:
Hi Riot,

Could you please provide me with my match history from Season 4 and 5? That would be awesome. Thank you.

Best,
Westen Night

replies.body: Thanks. The match history page was not loading previously but works now.

I can't directly provide your match history, but you can view match history on [**this page**](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/). You may not be able to view matches back from season 4 or 5, depending on how many matches you've played since then.

If you have any other questions, let me know.
